overview: As CEO and Co-Founder, Jeff Tseng is in business mode around the clock, leading a highly skilled team that is passionate about social analytics. No stranger to the startup world, Jeff has been involved in several early stage companies and has led a number of large research projects, investigating large-scale data processing and analytics, scalable architectures, wireless sensor networks, robotics, image compression, and system design. Prior to becoming a business leader, Jeff was a Ph.D. Electrical Engineering candidate at UCLA. His ambition and drive have been apparent since childhood - Jeff’s first entrepreneurial venture was a comic production he started with his cousin at the age of 13.
